   \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/commit/857960d3a71a82085b3fd3ec0caa265e5a984882\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"49f91b9835df7be53c3f0290c3205d8019275335\",\n    \"short_id\": \"49f91b98\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T11:25:18.000+07:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"da42f50758ee10cc204ed484cb8687607f3cf071\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"refactor: replace environment.ts with centralized env.helper.ts\",\n    \"message\": \"refactor: replace environment.ts with centralized env.helper.ts\\n\\n- Expand env.helper.ts with all variables: APP_NAME, NODE_ENV, PORT, SOCKET_PORT,\\n  FE_SERVER, LOG_LEVEL, LOG_OUTPUT_JSON, CREATE_SAMPLE_DB, LSC_OLD_VERSION,\\n  MONGODB_URI/NAME/USER/PASSWORD, REDIS_URI, JWT_PRIVATE_KEY/EXPIRES_IN/COOKIE_EXPIRES_IN,\\n  ADMIN_ACCOUNT/PASSWORD, FCM_TOKEN, CLOUDINARY_*\\n- Distinguish required (throws on missing) vs optional (has default) env vars\\n- Delete src/config/environment.ts (individual const exports pattern removed)\\n- Migrate all 12 importing files to use env object from env.helper.ts:\\n  server.ts, jwt.strategy.ts, token.service.ts, password.helper.ts,\\n  fcm.helper.ts, database.adapter.ts, redis.adapter.ts, logger.ts,\\n  initSeedData.ts, migration.ts, error.middleware.ts, morgan.middleware.ts\\n\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Ninh Thanh Khuong\",\n    \"author_email\": \"ninhem575@gmail.com\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-03-10T11:25:18.000+07:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Ninh Thanh Khuong\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"ninhem575@gmail.com\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-03-10T11:25:18.000+07:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/commit/49f91b9835df7be53c3f0290c3205d8019275335\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"acad09580650d6311688d489f97df718985f13fa\",\n    \"short_id\": \"acad0958\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T04:06:29.000+00:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"dab80089d95eb0ae2b0d8443e8f57344265a7e1e\",\n      \"da42f50758ee10cc204ed484cb8687607f3cf071\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"Merge branch 'feature/authentication-authorization' into 'refactor/main'\",\n    \"message\": \"Merge branch 'feature/authentication-authorization' into 'refactor/main'\\n\\ndocs(swagger): add full CRUD paths for studentComments, teacherComments, studentInfos, teacherInfos\\n\\nSee merge request ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend!153\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Hiếu Phạm Minh\",\n    \"author_email\": \"hieupm.98.tn@gmail.com\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-03-10T04:06:29.000+00:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Hiếu Phạm Minh\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"hieupm.98.tn@gmail.com\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-03-10T04:06:29.000+00:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/commit/acad09580650d6311688d489f97df718985f13fa\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"da42f50758ee10cc204ed484cb8687607f3cf071\",\n    \"short_id\": \"da42f507\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T11:02:58.000+07:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"afc5983dac25c9adc439f55ec0ceec07d38a1cda\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"docs(swagger): add full CRUD paths for studentComments, teacherComments, studentInfos, teacherInfos\",\n    \"message\": \"docs(swagger): add full CRUD paths for studentComments, teacherComments, studentInfos, teacherInfos\\n\\n- /student-comments: add /{id} GET, PATCH, DELETE; add pagination params; update tag to StudentComments\\n- /teacher-comments: add /{id} GET, PATCH, DELETE; add pagination params; update tag to TeacherComments\\n- /student-infos: add GET (paginated), POST, /all (no pagination), /{id} GET, PATCH, DELETE\\n- /teacher-infos: add POST, /ranking GET, /user/{userId} GET+DELETE, /{id} GET, PATCH, DELETE\\n\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Ninh Thanh Khuong\",\n    \"author_email\": \"ninhem575@gmail.com\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-03-10T11:02:58.000+07:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Ninh Thanh Khuong\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"ninhem575@gmail.com\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-03-10T11:02:58.000+07:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/commit/da42f50758ee10cc204ed484cb8687607f3cf071\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"dab80089d95eb0ae2b0d8443e8f57344265a7e1e\",\n    \"short_id\": \"dab80089\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T03:48:54.000+00:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"3542bdc1919e80f831b98e28b0153bf8b5e01928\",\n      \"afc5983dac25c9adc439f55ec0ceec07d38a1cda\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"Merge branch 'feature/authentication-authorization' into 'refactor/main'\",\n    \"message\": \"Merge branch 'feature/authentication-authorization' into 'refactor/main'\\n\\ndocs & refactor: update swagger, fix CSP for SwaggerUI, standardize IMeta responses\\n\\nSee merge request ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend!152\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Hiếu Phạm Minh\",\n    \"author_email\": \"hieupm.98.tn@gmail.com\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-03-10T03:48:54.000+00:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Hiếu Phạm Minh\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"hieupm.98.tn@gmail.com\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-03-10T03:48:54.000+00:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/commit/dab80089d95eb0ae2b0d8443e8f57344265a7e1e\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"afc5983dac25c9adc439f55ec0ceec07d38a1cda\",\n    \"short_id\": \"afc5983d\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T10:45:38.000+07:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"92606250a8fa2451c1cbdbd7def57a14e1a94490\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"about(fix-lint): implement handling fix lint!\",\n    \"message\": \"about(fix-lint): implement handling fix lint!\\n\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Ninh Thanh Khuong\",\n    \"author_email\": \"ninhem575@gmail.com\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-03-10T10:45:38.000+07:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Ninh Thanh Khuong\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"ninhem575@gmail.com\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-03-10T10:45:38.000+07:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/commit/afc5983dac25c9adc439f55ec0ceec07d38a1cda\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"92606250a8fa2451c1cbdbd7def57a14e1a94490\",\n    \"short_id\": \"92606250\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T10:33:02.000+07:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"1b197d13dc38c0a086e92a5ad8cbb1f4117866e4\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"docs & refactor: update swagger, fix CSP for SwaggerUI, standardize IMeta responses\",\n    \"message\": \"docs & refactor: update swagger, fix CSP for SwaggerUI, standardize IMeta responses\\n\\n- swagger.yaml: rewrite API docs with full endpoint coverage\\n  - Add common response schemas (Meta, BaseResponse, SingleResponse, ListResponse)\\n  - Add auth, users (nested: students, teachers, sales, leads), payments paths\\n  - Add vehicles, stadiums, lead-sources, lead-infos, internal-costs, dashboards paths\\n  - Add lessons, lesson-types, exams, exam-results, exam-schedules, exam-registrations, comments paths\\n  - Add all corresponding schemas (Vehicle, Stadium, LeadSource, LeadInfo, InternalCost, Lesson, Exam, etc.)\\n  - Remove outdated /user/student, /user/teacher, /student-info paths\\n\\n- src/app.ts: fix helmet CSP blocking SwaggerUI assets\\n  - Allow CSS/JS/fonts from unpkg.com and cdn.jsdelivr.net\\n  - Add imgSrc, fontSrc, workerSrc directives for full SwaggerUI support\\n\\n- payments: standardize paginated responses to IMeta interface\\n  - payments.service.ts: refactor list methods to return { docs, meta }\\n  - payments.controller.ts: use responseHandler.sendList with meta\\n  - payments.interface.ts: update IPaymentListResponse to use IMeta\\n\\n- users: standardize paginated responses to IMeta interface\\n  - users.service.ts: refactor list methods to return { docs, meta }\\n  - users.controller.ts: use responseHandler.sendList with meta\\n  - users.interface.ts: update list response interfaces to use IMeta\\n\\n- README.md: add comprehensive project documentation\\n\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Ninh Thanh Khuong\",\n    \"author_email\": \"ninhem575@gmail.com\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-03-10T10:33:02.000+07:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Ninh Thanh Khuong\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"ninhem575@gmail.com\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-03-10T10:33:02.000+07:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/commit/92606250a8fa2451c1cbdbd7def57a14e1a94490\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"3542bdc1919e80f831b98e28b0153bf8b5e01928\",\n    \"short_id\": \"3542bdc1\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T02:34:17.000+00:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"51e167cd16759422fc5b344daa98a906c111aecc\",\n      \"1b197d13dc38c0a086e92a5ad8cbb1f4117866e4\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"Merge branch 'feature/authentication-authorization' into 'refactor/main'\",\n    \"message\": \"Merge branch 'feature/authentication-authorization' into 'refactor/main'\\n\\nfix(appError): modifying logic throw status code (faile, error)!\\n\\nSee merge request ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend!151\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Hiếu Phạm Minh\",\n    \"author_email\": \"hieupm.98.tn@gmail.com\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-03-10T02:34:17.000+00:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Hiếu Phạm Minh\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"hieupm.98.tn@gmail.com\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-03-10T02:34:17.000+00:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend/-/commit/3542bdc1919e80f831b98e28b0153bf8b5e01928\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"1b197d13dc38c0a086e92a5ad8cbb1f4117866e4\",\n    \"short_id\": \"1b197d13\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-10T09:31:02.000+07:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"15279ed5ff932074ad1e0f063db287d865a03cbd\"\n    ],\n   