\\"97d7b91c-c3cb-473a-aa86-79cc9446445f\\\"><p local-id=\\\"2a6f3397-edea-4ffb-a980-d04f37480c5a\\\">VIETTQ</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"2240e972-7f2b-4bfe-befc-719a41f1a726\\\"><p local-id=\\\"e79c06ab-0ae6-4bb9-9314-89114b974dc3\\\">Quản l&yacute; leads</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"6dd613f9-e327-476c-8070-7361dae57dfb\\\"><p local-id=\\\"faa4b4b3-3c04-4200-bfc6-2a6a92e654b7\\\"><em><span style=\\\"color: rgb(151,160,175);\\\">A - Tạo mới</span></em></p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"92bd933a-f261-4103-b471-fbe1c73a0261\\\"><p local-id=\\\"55d43344-3cd4-42ab-a4e3-22af01567880\\\" /></td></tr></tbody></table><h1 local-id=\\\"a5e1fdfd-1529-47ba-b809-2e77aa9e9a9f\\\"><strong>I. DESCRIPTION</strong></h1><p local-id=\\\"b5799037-6e8a-472d-b78a-cb255a3c7964\\\">Quản l&yacute; leads cho ph&eacute;p người d&ugrave;ng (thường l&agrave; quản l&yacute; hoặc nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n kinh doanh) tạo mới, theo d&otilde;i v&agrave; cập nhật th&ocirc;ng tin của c&aacute;c lead (kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng) trong hệ thống. Mỗi lead sẽ chứa th&ocirc;ng tin cơ bản về kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng v&agrave; t&igrave;nh trạng chăm s&oacute;c/sales.</p><h2 local-id=\\\"18065012-834d-4b99-9d8b-9687a9499162\\\">ACTIVITY DIAGRAM</h2><ac:image ac:align=\\\"center\\\" ac:layout=\\\"center\\\" ac:original-height=\\\"559\\\" ac:original-width=\\\"1188\\\" ac:custom-width=\\\"true\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"28701cc7-2cec-4a60-9c01-be54d0bed52e\\\" ac:width=\\\"760\\\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\\\"{22DF871A-B771-4BC5-9954-B428C543233A}-20251230-014611.png\\\" ri:version-at-save=\\\"1\\\" /></ac:image><h2 local-id=\\\"3f5b9d79-ff5f-409d-9ffa-94a06121b576\\\">SEQUENCE DIAGRAM</h2><h2 local-id=\\\"116c9d4e-8e9c-474a-8490-9fb40cdf93de\\\">WIREFRAME</h2><p local-id=\\\"7ae5396d-fd08-4cea-b5fc-b6b95434e09e\\\" /><h2 local-id=\\\"1ca48be4-1e8b-41a3-9887-70fcb42ac0d9\\\">UI DESIGN</h2><ac:image ac:align=\\\"center\\\" ac:layout=\\\"wide\\\" ac:original-height=\\\"918\\\" ac:original-width=\\\"1919\\\" ac:custom-width=\\\"true\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"324dde94-73b1-4a85-8b68-b42af21743e3\\\" ac:alt=\\\"image-20250729-021342.png\\\" ac:width=\\\"1074\\\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\\\"image-20250729-021342.png\\\" ri:version-at-save=\\\"1\\\" /><ac:caption ac:local-id=\\\"5d3ddab9-6cd3-44f1-94e5-c5c060b08c75\\\"><p>Danh s&aacute;ch Leads</p></ac:caption></ac:image><p local-id=\\\"20ce56d8-edf6-40f0-bbe6-65ffe4c48301\\\" /><h2 local-id=\\\"1ab11b19-b778-4e73-ac0f-a814387993e6\\\">UI DESCRIPTION</h2><table data-table-width=\\\"1800\\\" data-layout=\\\"center\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"79597813-a841-41bb-bcee-3559544fe4cf\\\"><colgroup><col style=\\\"width: 364.0px;\\\" /><col style=\\\"width: 240.0px;\\\" /><col style=\\\"width: 194.0px;\\\" /><col style=\\\"width: 136.0px;\\\" /><col style=\\\"width: 134.0px;\\\" /><col style=\\\"width: 154.0px;\\\" /><col style=\\\"width: 571.0px;\\\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\\\"0e26a174-bb73-4c50-b128-815a1692b214\\\"><th data-highlight-colour=\\\"#f0f1f2\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"4ad48799-6d93-4e57-80c6-8d4ba50a0611\\\"><p local-id=\\\"0e1484c0-7e20-47ea-b645-e4622d695748\\\"><strong>Screen</strong></p></th><th data-highlight-colour=\\\"#f0f1f2\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"c93f6ab6-9c1e-490f-b0ab-7fa1b92e7763\\\"><p local-id=\\\"ae4baf14-fff5-4484-8ff8-74af87e73180\\\"><strong>Funtion/Component</strong></p></th><th data-highlight-colour=\\\"#f0f1f2\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"7f4e523c-a3a1-4205-8647-00cdc7e4772c\\\"><p local-id=\\\"422599d5-29e6-425e-8280-6f6326892f47\\\"><strong>Control</strong></p></th><th data-highlight-colour=\\\"#f0f1f2\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"f97f7b2b-bb7d-4c51-a92c-de43f7c32991\\\"><p local-id=\\\"21d0baf2-c09d-4edb-960d-cbc0f2662861\\\"><strong>Data type</strong></p></th><th data-highlight-colour=\\\"#f0f1f2\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"011b879c-0bb6-44f5-85dd-079892d359df\\\"><p local-id=\\\"facd291d-341d-469e-b137-320b9b3d7c77\\\"><strong>Require</strong></p></th><th data-highlight-colour=\\\"#f0f1f2\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"7cc5c3c5-0c15-4521-926e-d5f719b0110b\\\"><p local-id=\\\"08ba35a6-4956-4518-82dd-ed7931943aa8\\\"><strong>Condition</strong></p></th><th data-highlight-colour=\\\"#f0f1f2\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"660d889e-b120-4528-8aed-af4ac0258086\\\"><p local-id=\\\"44fb16b0-7905-4ebf-b7c4-703405281502\\\"><strong>Description</strong></p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"558edf90-a6e5-4bfd-b5f9-8789578fe42a\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"86ee8a1a-03a0-426a-babb-f1e5af0266f1\\\"><ac:image ac:align=\\\"center\\\" ac:layout=\\\"center\\\" ac:original-height=\\\"51\\\" ac:original-width=\\\"89\\\" ac:custom-width=\\\"true\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"31db5105-3a53-4808-8717-0d65b7684756\\\" ac:alt=\\\"image-20250729-082101.png\\\" ac:width=\\\"89\\\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\\\"image-20250729-082101.png\\\" ri:version-at-save=\\\"1\\\" /></ac:image><p local-id=\\\"5e725920-88f2-4e99-861b-d1c8ce2756fe\\\" /></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"286415ea-af51-4294-b834-6ddc29836ddf\\\"><p local-id=\\\"5d05c939-9bc5-4332-9d63-20c45cd2ee8e\\\">Tạo lead</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"510179e3-d713-445d-b88a-bd2befe8fd98\\\"><p local-id=\\\"748ab90c-a7b5-4035-85cb-f1bb6ad5e975\\\">Button</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"97f86adc-6a1a-40e1-98d3-5689fa96f879\\\"><p local-id=\\\"da1353c9-8ce0-49b6-bd58-8b9ae08e81ee\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"e5d26302-6068-4df4-8854-20f06bc0509c\\\"><p local-id=\\\"5a7579de-b956-4fd0-9bb1-5a3d61247f8e\\\">Y</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"40aee848-85eb-4b85-9050-95f5dcde73ee\\\"><p local-id=\\\"7ba134ac-993c-4625-90ac-341c0cc7616e\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"9a93c257-e407-4c4a-b5a1-159ee60fc615\\\"><p local-id=\\\"ad32db4c-33ee-4abc-9c76-96b5c23a8db8\\\">Cho ph&eacute;p người d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; thể th&ecirc;m mới được kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng để tư vấn về dịch vụ của m&igrave;nh</p><p local-id=\\\"fdc0b74a-a5c8-467f-b4bd-478e8680da6a\\\"><strong>OnClick:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"31cd699a-1e60-4547-aa3c-99869499d1fd\\\">Chuyển hướng đến trang &ldquo;Th&ecirc;m mới kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng tiềm năng&rdquo;</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"6e37b9a1-f9ed-4093-a5a2-a7105733bd72\\\"><td rowspan=\\\"7\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"c169d10b-fd88-406d-a304-3d0a4c736a5a\\\"><ac:image ac:align=\\\"center\\\" ac:layout=\\\"center\\\" ac:original-height=\\\"227\\\" ac:original-width=\\\"1798\\\" ac:custom-width=\\\"true\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"a965688e-0421-41f6-be30-0bd8fa51d627\\\" ac:alt=\\\"image-20250729-023451.png\\\" ac:width=\\\"163\\\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\\\"image-20250729-023451.png\\\" ri:version-at-save=\\\"1\\\" /><ac:caption ac:local-id=\\\"254b0eb5-035a-48ed-bdb7-40e790933657\\\"><p>Bộ lọc</p></ac:caption></ac:image></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"ff15215d-414d-41db-a0c7-3df6da9033a2\\\"><p local-id=\\\"01df3a51-95c2-4d4a-bced-ddc1b1848570\\\">T&ecirc;n</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"3ee84aa5-a89e-4974-a602-43df79d78e56\\\"><p local-id=\\\"45e69393-c6e7-4959-a3d4-ac71d4c28166\\\">Textbox</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"40f4bfb3-9147-4389-bbde-cc7b92a5a9b0\\\"><p local-id=\\\"29dbe162-f91d-4570-8bc3-038a1b120c23\\\">Text</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"c4132f23-aab9-47e2-b155-bc6f977bb815\\\"><p local-id=\\\"1287e146-80ec-47dd-832b-5e5586537127\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"d17ff9cf-9676-4c93-bb9f-2afcfc2b82fa\\\"><p local-id=\\\"a3ec7637-3cc2-4822-9920-cb385ca28a54\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"c684f3f6-d07e-4af5-a458-754d88b8f1b1\\\"><p local-id=\\\"83042ecb-fc4c-470e-8797-5304b5451b54\\\"><strong>Default value:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"58db86fc-bbb9-41ae-bee4-2226bda467ff\\\">Hint text hiển thị &ldquo;Nhập t&ecirc;n&rdquo;</p><p local-id=\\\"e7197535-009d-44e5-8347-238bbb806ac5\\\"><strong>OnClick:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"c1fcdf28-9909-4de6-ba09-4a19a5579498\\\">Nhập t&ecirc;n leads muốn t&igrave;m kiếm &rarr; Click button &ldquo;T&igrave;m kiếm&rdquo; or Enter:</p><ul local-id=\\\"525f6e1f-c1a1-464d-95ba-7662c4e1ba73\\\"><li local-id=\\\"421d1496-ed44-493e-91cc-fcf8ead6e743\\\"><p local-id=\\\"35849935-3b67-4723-a387-e3d6b1c95e48\\\">TH1: C&oacute; dữ liệu &rarr; Hiển thị dữ liệu lọc được ở bảng danh s&aacute;ch leads</p></li><li local-id=\\\"72d3e441-8b7e-4d27-b194-79557d15038b\\\"><p local-id=\\\"1d0003ae-ac21-46f3-9b1f-5a8fa62535f4\\\">TH2: Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; dữ liệu &rarr; Hiển thị text &ldquo;Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; dữ liệu&rdquo; ở bảng danh s&aacute;ch leads</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\\\"7d4a8f62-c6cc-4f50-8e80-1cddcf80f2d8\\\"><td ac:local-id=\\\"de22cf3a-30aa-4dae-9933-0b1203543058\\\"><p local-id=\\\"ed3d2482-5dc3-41a9-b155-6fee1d0483d1\\\">Người phụ tr&aacute;ch</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"fd0ce694-01b9-45ca-a49d-40e067f48c43\\\"><p local-id=\\\"a6a237d2-8a96-470f-974d-dd151429f669\\\">Dropdown button</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"b262fabc-8fb7-496c-9b7f-b16c25340546\\\"><p local-id=\\\"d18df2c9-b6b2-46fe-be24-a07ebde51b8b\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"61d53dbb-bb76-4c23-8190-53b253b15a1d\\\"><p local-id=\\\"b95e766c-190e-4c43-9f29-e33e1cbf4df4\\\">Y</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"5f409871-582c-4aa6-bf3d-0383a241a2df\\\"><p local-id=\\\"ddc35e6e-dcde-4b61-9e68-f0c8f6419c91\\\">-</p></td><td ac:local-id=\\\"ef43090b-334b-400b-8347-210de86947b7\\\"><p local-id=\\\"47089536-37d4-4090-8ed2-32476eca801c\\\"><strong>Require: </strong></p><p local-id=\\\"887878b7-ef27-4291-b5c2-dfd402c1e3af\\\">List được danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c bạn sale trong dropdown</p><p local-id=\\\"69d8e937-12c2-44e6-8130-5cfb5422b9dd\\\"><strong>Default value:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"4c88768a-bc03-4a90-9199-d701e1ec9159\\\">Hint text hiển thị &ldquo;Chọn người phụ tr&aacute;ch&rdquo;</p><p local-id=\\\"aefab168-8f03-49ac-9e9c-bedc400f5f33\\\"><strong>OnClick:</strong></p><p local-id=\\\"abe32a14-9ed2-4fac-a15c-125fd895f931\\\">Dropdown c&aacute;c bạn sale trong danh s&aacute;ch sale</p><ac:image ac:align=\\\"center\\\" ac:layout=\\\"center\\\" ac:original-height=\\\"259\\\" ac:original-width=\\\"401\\\" ac:custom-width=\\\"true\\\" ac:local-id=\\\"2ee72b24-455e-4055-ba72-8a7c74ca8c63\\\" ac:alt=\\\"image-20250729-080939.png\\\" ac:width=\