{"type":"message","id":"8c1775d9","parentId":"137d13b8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:47:02.209Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is reporting that the registration feature is not working - after registering, they can't log in with the email and password they used to register. This is a bug in the QLHV project.\n\nLet me investigate the auth/registration flow in both BE and FE to understand what's happening.\n\nFirst, I need to check the backend auth registration endpoint and the frontend registration form.","thinkingSignature":"027546e6d0489aa643a1dabdfac1559dd702fefa7af569db1cab5c32a20a39c5"},{"type":"text","text":"Rõ rồi. Đăng ký xong nhưng đăng nhập không được — có vấn đề ở auth flow. Để tôi điều tra.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5304y0d1mslp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src -name \"*.ts\" | xargs grep -l -i \"register\\|signup\\|auth\" 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5304y0d1mslp_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src -name \"*.tsx\" | xargs grep -l -i \"register\\|signup\\|auth\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":43,"output":262,"cacheRead":98943,"cacheWrite":1536,"totalTokens":100784,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776044813962,"responseId":"062b7e0f6c1342a119c7e38b65dead26"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c9d6d75","parentId":"8c1775d9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:47:02.635Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5304y0d1mslp_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/middlewares/rbac.middleware.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/middlewares/system_log.middleware.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/middlewares/rate-limit.middleware.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/middlewares/auth.middleware.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/routes/index.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/routes/auth.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/routes/vip_qr.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/routes/settings.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/dashboard.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/auth.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/dtos/auth.dto.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/scripts/seed_practical_students.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/scripts/migrate_notifications.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlh