{"type":"message","id":"95a05ce8","parentId":"8b65fd39","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:19:37.373Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3ra4jsolug6o_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"'use client';\n\nimport React, { useState } from 'react';\n\nexport const Settingspanel: React.FC = () => {\n  const [regions, setRegions] = useState('Hanoi, HCM, Da Nang');\n  const [licenseTypes, setLicenseTypes] = useState('A1, B1, B2, C');\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6\">\n      <h2 className=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-6\">System Settings</h2>\n      \n      <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n        <div>\n          <label className=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">Regions</label>\n          <input \n            value={regions} onChange={(e) => setRegions(e.target.value)}\n            className=\"w-full p-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary\"\n          />\n        </div>\n        \n        <div>\n          <label className=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1\">License Types</label>\n          <input \n            value={licenseTypes} onChange={(e) => setLicenseTypes(e.target.value)}\n            className=\"w-full p-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary\"\n          />\n        </div>\n\n        <button className=\"bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-700\">\n          Save Changes\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n};\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776050377292}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb74d3ea","parentId":"95a05ce8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:19:46.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the issue! The `Settingspanel.tsx` has hardcoded values for `licenseTypes`:\n```javascript\nconst [licenseTypes, setLicenseTypes] = useState('A1, B1, B2, C');\n```\n\nIt's not fetching from the database at all. The settings page needs to:\n1. Call a backend API to get the license types\n2. Display them properly\n\nLet me also check if there's a backend endpoint for license types and a settings service on the frontend.","thinkingSignature":"d78f1efd3197f218b6a9f0388039ae1523af1c1ba7ffb76dc6d4697c887092d7"},{"type":"text","text":"Tìm ra rồi! **Bug:** `licenseTypes` đang hardcoded:\n\n```typescript\nconst [licenseTypes, setLicenseTypes] = useState('A1, B1, B2, C');\n```\n\nKhông gọi database. Để tôi kiểm tra thêm BE có API nào cho license types chưa.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ot4sbuxsmwpy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src -name \"*.ts\" | xargs grep -l -i \"license\\|hang_bang\\|bang_lai\\|license_type\" 2>/dev/null | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ot4sbuxsmwpy_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/ | grep -i \"setting\\|license\\|bang\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":472,"output":316,"cacheRead":136262,"cacheWrite":820,"totalTokens":137870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776050377382,"responseId":"062b93cb8b7ab0ef506a56f97cbad050"}}
