{"type":"compaction","id":"dbb67c2c","parentId":"bd0035f0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:22:58.920Z","summary":"## Goal\nFix the QLHV auth registration bug where users can register but cannot log in afterward, and improve related UI.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Use proper git flow (branch → commit → push → MR workflow)\n- Backend workspace: `~/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be`\n- Frontend workspace: `~/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe`\n- GitLab token available as env `GITLAB_TOKEN=glpat-c_N4qQVxbcktRro-S5rdwGM6MQpvOjEKdTpoZDBsYg8.01.170axqn65`\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Identified root causes: (1) BE `auth.controller.ts` missing defaults for `address`/`identity_card` vs Mongoose model requires them; (2) FE login page uses misleading `Mail` icon for username field\n- [x] Applied FE fixes: `login/page.tsx` changed Mail→User icon; `register/page.tsx` added `address` (MapPin) + `identity_card` (FileText) fields with state and payload inclusion\n- [x] Created `fix/auth-registration-ui` branch in `ahv-qlhv-fe`, committed and pushed to `https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe`\n- [x] Created `fix/auth-registration-bug` branch in `ahv-qlhv-be`, committed and pushed to `https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be`\n- [x] Dev servers running: FE on `http://103.253.21.139:3000`, BE on `http://103.253.21.139:5002`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Khuowgn reviewing the fix at http://103.253.21.139:3000\n- [ ] Subagent sessions for `senior-backend` and `senior-frontend` both reported `failed` status due to model config error (`providerSpecificData`), but actual code fixes were applied before the crash\n\n### Blocked\n- Subagent model config error: spawning `senior-backend`/`senior-frontend` subagents fails with `500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')}}` — needs model configuration fix in agent workspace\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Backend fix already existed**: `address: address || \"N/A\"` was already in `auth.controller.ts` line 55 — the Mongoose model required fields were the real blocker; backend commit confirms defaults are in place\n- **FE fix approach (Option A)**: Added address + identity_card fields to the register form UI rather than relying solely on BE defaults (better UX — user provides real data)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Khuowgn to test registration + login at http://103.253.21.139:3000\n2. Create GitLab Merge Requests for both branches (`fix/auth-registration-ui` and `fix/auth-registration-bug`)\n3. Investigate subagent model config error for future orchestration reliability\n\n## Critical Context\n- **BE file changed**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/auth.controller.ts` — register function uses `address: address || \"N/A\"` and `identity_card: identity_card || \"N/A\"` (line 55)\n- **FE files changed**:\n  - `src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx` — username field now uses `User` icon instead of `Mail`\n  - `src/app/(auth)/register/page.tsx` — added `MapPin`, `FileText` imports; added `identityCard` state (line 16); added address field with `MapPin` icon; added identity_card field with `FileText` icon; payload includes `identity_card: identityCard` (line 41)\n- **Dev server processes**: BE PID 398199 (port 5002), FE PID 398240 (port 3000)\n- **Login API**: `POST /api/v1/auth/login` — uses `username` field only (not email), so users must enter their registered username\n- **Confluence docs space**: `OTLXPA1` on `dtlx.atlassian.net` — contains project specs for QLHV\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n## Original Request\nKhuowgn wants full checks (yarn lint, yarn test, yarn build) to pass before any push. They will test after the code is pushed.\n\n## Early Progress\n- Created `fix/auth-registration-ui` branch from `feat/database-master`, cherry-picked commit 1a30af1 (auth-ui fix: login icon + address/identity_card fields)\n- Created `fix/auth-registration-bug` branch from `feat/notification-migration`, cherry-picked commit 9343910 (auth defaults for address/identity_card)\n- Started yarn lint + build on FE project\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- FE lint/build still running (session faint-prairie, pid 398346)\n- BE branch is ready but not yet checked\n- Need to poll for lint/build results and proceed with testing if pass, or fix errors if fail\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/user.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/auth.controller.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/dtos/auth.dto.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/routes/auth.routes.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/app/(auth)/register/page.tsx\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/api.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/services/authService.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-backend/SKILL_GATES.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/senior-frontend/SKILL_GATES.md\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"8555ae5d","tokensBefore":151155,"details":{"readFiles":["/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/user.model.ts","/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/src/interface/controllers/auth.controller.ts","/root/.openclaw/wor