{"type":"message","id":"01fa92c5","parentId":"ee1be7d7","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:26:00.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to make sure the `handleSaveLicense` function works with the new `LicenseCategory` type from the new service. The `handleSaveLicense` function currently uses `LicenseCategory` from `settingsService.ts` (aliased as `LcSys`). But now there's also `LicenseCategory` from `licenseCategoryService.ts`.\n\nWait, I imported `LicenseCategory as LcSys` from settingsService and `LicenseCategory` from licenseCategoryService. In the `handleSaveLicense` function, the `data` parameter is `LicenseCategory` — but from which import?\n\nLooking at the code:\n```typescript\nconst handleSaveLicense = async (data: LicenseCategory) => {\n\n\n```\n\n`LicenseCategory` here refers to the last import, which is from `licenseCategoryService.ts`. But the modal (`LicenseModal`) uses `LicenseCategory` from `settingsService.ts`. Let me check the SettingsModals imports. The SettingsModals.tsx imports `LicenseCategory` from settingsService, so there's a type mismatch between what the modal uses and what the handler expects. This needs to be resolved.\n\nLooking at the actual usage, the `LicenseCategory` from settingsService has fields like `id`, `type`, `name`, `fee`, `tags`, `inactive`, and `dat`, while the new service's `LicenseCategory` has `id`, `code`, `name`, `description`, `type`, `fee`, `tags`, `inactive`, and `dat`. They're similar enough that the save handler should work with either version since they share the essential fields.\n\n```\n\ntypescript\nconst handleSaveLicense = async (data: LicenseCategory) => {\n```\n\nNow this refers to the new `LicenseCategory` from `licenseCategoryService.ts`. But the modal (`LicenseModal`) uses the old one from `settingsService.ts`. The old `LicenseCategory` interface has `id`, `type`, `name`, `fee`, `tags`, `inactive`, and `dat`, while the new one adds `code` and `description` — so the new interface is a superset of the old one.\n\nThe real issue is that `handleSaveLicense` updates `settings.license_categories`, but now that we have a separate `licensecategories` collection, we should be saving directly to that instead. Since the modal works with the old interface, I'll keep it compatible and make sure the save handler correctly maps the data to the new collection.","thinkingSignature":"51962b5df9e4954c37086077617200fdbc3d188c4c968b6b620ef42c71f8b93b"},{"type":"text","text":"Giờ update `handleSaveLicense` để lưu vào collection `licensecategories` mới thay vì settings:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1bd0838scnl9_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-fe/src/app/settings/page.tsx","edits":[{"oldText":"import { getSystemSettings, updateSystemSettings, SystemSettings, LicenseCategory as LcSys, Clinic as ClinicType } from '@/src/services/settingsService';\nimport { getLicenseCategories, LicenseCategory } from '@/src/services/licenseCategoryService';","newText":"import { getSystemSettings, updateSystemSettings, SystemSettings, Clinic as ClinicType } from '@/src/services/settingsService';\nimport { getLicenseCategories, LicenseCategory } from '@/src/services/licenseCategoryService';"},{"oldText":"import { getCities, createCity, updateCity, deleteCity, City } from '@/src/services/cityService';","newText":"import { getCities, createCity, updateCity, deleteCity, City } from '@/src/services/cityService';\nimport { createLicenseCategory, updateLicenseCategory, deleteLicenseCategory } from '@/src/services/licenseCategoryService';"},{"oldText":"  const handleSaveLicense = async (data: LicenseCategory) => {\n    try {\n      const currentSettings = systemSettings || { license_categories: [] };\n      let updatedLicenses = [...(currentSettings.license_categories || [])];\n      if (editingLicense) {\n        updatedLicenses = updatedLicenses.map(l => l.id === editingLicense.id ? data : l);\n      } else {\n        if (updatedLicenses.find(l => l.id === data.id)) {\n          toast.error('Mã hạng bằng đã tồn tại');\n          return;\n        }\n        updatedLicenses.push(data);\n      }\n\n      const res = await updateSystemSettings({ license_categories: updatedLicenses });\n      if (res.success) {\n        toast.success('Đã lưu hạng bằng');\n        setSystemSettings(prev => prev ? { ...prev, license_categories: updatedLicenses } : { license_categories: updatedLicenses } as any);\n        setIsLicenseOpen(false);\n      } else {\n        toast.error(res.message || 'Lỗi khi lưu hạng bằng');\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      toast.error('Lỗi khi lưu hạng bằng');\n    }\n  };","newText":"  const handleSaveLicense = async (data: LicenseCategory) => {\n    try {\n      if (editingLicense) {\n        const res = await updateLicenseCategory(editingLicense.id, data);\n        if (res.success) {\n          toast.success('Đã cập nhật hạng bằng');\n          const lcRes = await getLicenseCategories();\n          if (lcRes.success) setLicenseCategories(Array.isArray(lcRes.data) ? lcRes.data : []);\n          setIsLicenseOpen(false);\n        } else {\n          toast.error(res.message || 'Lỗi khi cập nhật hạng bằng');\n        }\n      } else {\n        const res = await createLicenseCategory(data);\n        if (res.success) {\n          toast.success('Đã thêm hạng bằng');\n          const lcRes = await getLicenseCategories();\n          if (lcRes.success) setLicenseCategories(Array.isArray(lcRes.data) ? lcRes.data : []);\n          setIsLicenseOpen(false);\n        } else {\n          toast.error(res.message || 'Lỗi khi thêm hạng bằng');\n        }\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      toast.error('Lỗi khi lưu hạng bằng');\n    }\n  };"},{"oldText":"    if (type === 'license' && systemSettings) {\n      const updated = (systemSettings.license_categories || []).filter(l => l.id !== id);\n      const res = await updateSystemSettings({ license_categories: updated });\n      if (res.success) {\n        setSystemSettings({ ...systemSettings, license_categories: updated });\n        toast.success('Đã xóa hạng bằng');\n      }\n    }","newText":"    if (type === 'license') {\n      const res = await deleteLicenseCategory(id);\n      if (res.success) {\n        setLicenseCategories(prev => prev.filter(l => l.id !== id));\n        toast.success('Đã xóa hạng bằng');\n      }\n    }"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":157,"output":1608,"cacheRead":48045,"cacheWrite":1106,"totalTokens":50916,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776050728669,"responseId":"062b95291cedfda52c1ca7e9d0cd7f4b"}}
