{"type":"message","id":"ee872f8f","parentId":"885c43fa","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:42:33.234Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API is working perfectly! It returns license categories from the database. Now I can see the fix is working. Let me now commit and push the changes.\n\nActually wait - the user is testing. Let me just report what was done and say the dev servers are running. The API is working correctly.\n\nNow let me commit all the changes. I need to:\n1. Commit BE changes (new license-category route files)\n2. Commit FE changes (new service, updated settings page)\n3. Force push to the branches\n\nActually, the user might want to test first before I push. Let me report the fix and then commit after they confirm it works.","thinkingSignature":"ead5ce459a4b1dde8c9220a7a749998b142592faab2acf573e8cd76b615be61b"},{"type":"text","text":"API đang hoạt động ✅ Đổ dữ liệu thật từ DB:\n\n```json\n{\"success\":true,\"data\":[\n  {\"id\":\"...\",\"code\":\"A\",\"name\":\"Hạng A\",\"type\":\"Xe máy\",...},\n  {\"id\":\"...\",\"code\":\"A1\",\"name\":\"Hạng A1\",\"type\":\"Xe máy\",...},\n  {\"id\":\"...\",\"code\":\"B1\",\"name\":\"Hạng B1\",\"type\":\"Ô tô\",...},\n  ...\n]}\n```\n\n**Tóm tắt fix:**\n\n| File | Thay đổi |\n|------|---------|\n| BE — `license-category.routes.ts` | API mới: GET/POST/PUT/DELETE `/license-categories` |\n| BE — `license-category.controller.ts` | Controller xử lý CRUD |\n| BE — `license-category.service.ts` | Đọc từ collection `licensecategories` (đã seed sẵn) |\n| FE — `licenseCategoryService.ts` | Service mới gọi API trên |\n| FE — `settings/page.tsx` | Gọi `getLicenseCategories()`, dùng data thật thay vì rỗng |\n\nDev servers đang chạy:\n- **FE**: http://103.253.21.139:3000/settings → **Chung → Hạng bằng**\n- **BE**: http://103.253.21.139:5002\n\nBạn test thử, nếu OK tôi commit + push lên GitLab."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":374