{"type":"message","id":"3be5b550","parentId":"af4c0384","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:43:58.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, both pushed. Now let me create/update the MRs. The FE MR !10 already exists. I should check the BE MR. The `fix/auth-registration-bug` branch MR doesn't seem to have been created yet. Let me create it.\n\nActually, the BE push said \"To create a merge request for fix/auth-registration-bug, visit: https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be/-/merge_requests/new?merge_request%5Bsource_branch%5D=fix%2Fauth-registration-bug\" - so no MR was auto-created. Let me create one.","thinkingSignature":"f6ceb8e7b79d64ae2bb4dd82d60be5a6fcf31df8f262061587ffddb9269656e8"},{"type":"text","text":"Cả hai đã push ✅ Tạo MR cho BE:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zy1obsn1mbwz_1","name":"gitlab__gitlab_create_merge_request","arguments":{"project_id":"81078323","source_branch":"fix/auth-registration-bug","target_branch":"develop","title":"fix(settings): add license-categories CRUD API + auth defaults","description":"## Summary\n- Add `LicenseCategoryService` reading from `licensecategories` collection\n- Add full CRUD endpoint: `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/license-categories`\n- Fix BE default values for `address` and `identity_card` in register\n\n## Test\n- [ ] `GET /api/v1/license-categories` returns seeded license data\n- [ ] Settings page shows real license categories"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":208,"output":324,"cacheRead":67038,"cacheWrite":723,"totalTokens":68293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776051827188,"responseId":"062b997525337f4a83b12c409317d952"}}
{"type":"message","id":"77e39d9b","parentId":"3be5b550","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:43:59.336Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zy1obsn1mbwz_1","toolName":"gitlab__gitlab_create_merge_request","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": 473134087,\n  \"iid\": 7,\n  \"project_id\": 81078323,\n  \"title\": \"fix(settings): add license-categories CRUD API + auth defaults\",\n  \"description\": \"## Summary\\n- Add `LicenseCategoryService` reading from `licensecategories` collection\\n- Add full CRUD endpoint: `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/license-categories`\\n- Fix BE default values for `address` and `identity_card` in register\\n\\n## Test\\n- [ ] `GET /api/v1/license-categories` returns seeded license data\\n- [ ] Settings page shows real license categories\",\n  \"state\": \"opened\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-04-13T03:43:58.940Z\",\n  \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-13T03:43:58.940Z\",\n  \"merged_by\": null,\n  \"merge_user\": null,\n  \"merged_at\": null,\n  \"closed_by\": null,\n  \"closed_at\": null,\n  \"target_branch\": \"develop\",\n  \"source_branch\": \"fix/auth-registration-bug\",\n  \"user_notes_count\": 0,\n  \"upvotes\": 0,\n  \"downvotes\": 0,\n  \"author\": {\n    \"id\": 29160767,\n    \"username\": \"ninhkhuongpl7\",\n    \"public_email\": null,\n    \"name\": \"khuong ninh\",\n    \"state\": \"active\",\n    \"locked\": false,\n    \"avatar_url\": \"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0272ae77fdbd1dc20257bb15df743e9271352040c8fecc313ab6b4649211a7f8?s=80&d=identicon\",\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ninhkhuongpl7\"\n  },\n  \"assignees\": [],\n  \"assignee\": null,\n  \"reviewers\": [],\n  \"source_project_id\": 81078323,\n  \"target_project_id\": 81078323,\n  \"labels\": [],\n  \"draft\": false,\n  \"imported\": false,\n  \"imported_from\": \"none\",\n  \"work_in_progress\": false,\n  \"milestone\": null,\n  \"merge_when_pipeline_succeeds\": false,\n  \"merge_status\": \"checking\",\n  \"detailed_merge_status\": \"pre