{"type":"message","id":"3b5430e8","parentId":"142f8d88","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:46:40.744Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now for the current fix - I need to make sure both branches are synced with develop before the next push. The current push already happened. For the MRs that are already created, I should also update them to be based on the latest develop.\n\nLet me also check the current status of the branches to see if they're behind.","thinkingSignature":"59a47e8a175684798df1f2993ab540680162f42c6ebe7e25b8423f9c0f31b12b"},{"type":"text","text":"Ghi nhớ rồi. Từ giờ trở đi, mỗi lần push sẽ luôn merge `origin/develop` trước."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":124,"output":114,"cacheRead":69456,"cacheWrite":799,"totalTokens":70493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776051991111,"responseId":"062b9a1a9b9a74ada308c7205face531"}}
